First: Happy Mahvelous Fourth of July.  Second: It is 8:27 pm, and it is still long from dark.  Third: I am spending this great day with a load of people, most of whom, I do not know. Yes, I am spending it with Scott's family and friends. Yes, they originate mostly from Oildale.  Fourth: Oildale = 93308 (The '08) = Oh the Redneckyness. Yes. Rednecks. Insert a load of Jeff Foxworthy jokes. By the way, all of them are true.  Fifth: It is finally getting dark, so I must be brave and enter the world of the overpriced, short-lived fireworks, and once again, as I am slowly learning to love, the Rednecks...